{"tid":2033020,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"利奧坊．曦岸開售：首推88個單位　年輕客為主","createTime":"2020-05-24T11:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T11:40:51.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e357107a1796d32ff6f1da25091d06e652cf1d2","tid":2033020,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:39:38.000Z","msg":"利奧坊．曦岸開售：首推88個單位 年輕客為主<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200524/photo/bkn-20200524123801497-0524_00842_001_01p.jpg?20200524141000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200524%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200524123801497-0524_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20200524141000&h=6c65b4a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各區新盤連環開售。恒基地產(00012)旗下旺角利奧坊&middot;曦岸周日(24日)首度發售88個單位，發展商正安排準買家排隊前售樓處揀樓。該盤昨日截止接受認購，市場料共錄約480張入票登記，超額認購逾4倍。據悉，大部分入票人士為年輕客，每名買家於首輪銷售最多可購2伙。"},{"pid":"b82942565a41ae6a412e3fedd947673e31288625","tid":2033020,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:39:43.000Z","msg":"連登仔又登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a62d9f141ce4848b9fb182fe1d0b6ec90b66fe","tid":2033020,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:40:22.000Z","msg":"右邊大眼妹好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eea0a199ffbde56167f30e19f8b0a06d2f247e0","tid":2033020,"uid":196329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b82942565a41ae6a412e3fedd947673e31288625","tid":2033020,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:39:43.000Z","msg":"連登仔又登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"全部都係地產商請人排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再唔係就屌佢地on9短視唔似cctoy精英